{
  "texts": [
    "The authors introduced influence estimation method in order to identify sentences that needs feedback.",
    "Hellman et al. (2020) proposed an approach called kNN-MIL, which employs k-nearest neighbor (kNN) and multi-instance learning (MIL) models for determining the impact of each sentence in the overall score of the essay.",
    "An essay is divided into sentences and each sentence is scored against rubrics to determine its contribution using kNN.",
    "This process identifies the sentences that discuss specific topics and rubric designated points across the essay.",
    "The aggregated score from the sentences is used to create a document-level holistic score."
  ]
}